    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable driver that needs some cosmetic attention. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows its age with some noticeable interior wear and several exterior scuffs and minor dings. It has been regularly serviced, but expect to invest in some minor repairs and a deep clean to bring it back to its best. It's a dependable car with plenty of life left for the right owner.",
