    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips occasionally, while the exterior shows heavy rusting and several large dents. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are inconsistent. It is best suited as a project car or for someone looking for a major restoration project.",
