    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is looking for a new owner who can give it the TLC it needs. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a fantastic, affordable foundation for anyone who loves a good restoration or needs a budget-friendly fixer-upper. Take this chance to bring some life back into this ride!",
      "price": 4500.0,
